#define pb push_back
#define mp make_pair
#define ll long long
#define vi vector<int>
#define all(x) x.begin(),x.end()

int main() {
	ios::sync_with_stdio(0);
	cin.tie(0);
	int t; cin >> t;
	while (t--) {
		int n; cin >> n;
		vi v;
		while (n--) {
			int x; cin >>x;
			v.pb(x);
		}
		sort(all(v));
		int flag = 0;
		for (int i = 1; i < v.size(); ++i) {
			if (v[i] == v[i - 1]) {
				cout << "NO\n";
				flag = 1;
				break;
			}
		}
		if (!flag) cout << "YES\n";
	}

	return 0;
}
